highlights.text: Sabrina Carpenter has the most spots on Top Songs Australia. “Tears” is the highest at #3.
“Mr. Brightside” by The Killers has been on Top Songs Australia the longest, at 454 weeks straight.
“Tears” by Sabrina Carpenter is the highest new entry on Top Songs Australia at #3.
“Up Down (Do This All Day) (feat. B.o.B)” by T-Pain and B.o.B is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Australia, up 54 spots at #79.
